  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This interventional study seeks to evaluate the overall outcomes of a novel, emotional
      awareness intervention for people with chronic musculoskeletal pain and determine which
      patients benefit the most from this intervention. The investigators also are evaluating the
      effects of brief emotional communication technique embedded in the pre-treatment assessment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
